#MOBILES
#11300
shadowloo officer~
a Shadowloo Officer~
An officer of the Shadowloo force stands, keeping the peace.
~
This fellow is equiped nicely with a sidearm and dressed in a formal uniform.
The decorations on this officers uniform suggest that he is a fairly distinguished
individual. He paces back and forth here scanning the area for those that are
not permitted into Shadowloo. His eyes meet yours, and he quickly begins
to pace towards your position.
~
