vega handsome man strong~
Vega~
A strong and handsome man stands here admiring himself.
~
Dressed in a very elaborate 'bull-fighting' outfit, Vega stands before
you, admiring himself in your presence. His red sash to his side adds a 
little flavor to his combat suit. He glares at you and begins to sharpen
his foot long claw. He teases you a bit by signaling you to come to
him, then he leaps high in the air and begins his attack!
~
