sagat man huge~
Sagat~
A huge man is here practicing his unique moves.
~
As you look upon him, Sagat turns and looks at you and grins. He is 
wearing an eye-patch on his right eye and has a massive battle scar on 
his chest. The battle scar seems to be inflicted by another individual, as
the scar isnt straight or very smooth along the edges. He leaps in the air
with a fierce dragon punch scream 'tiger uppercut!!'
~
