#11305
strong intelligent man m.bison bison~
M.Bison~
A strong and intelligent looking man stares at you as you enter.
~
Dressed in a red suit containing metal shoulder plates and leg plates,
M.Bison stands here with a blue aura around his body. This flame seems to
move at his commands instinctively. He gathers a ball of fire and begins to
approach you, snickering as he draws towards your location.
~
