instructor~
an Instructor~
An instructor for the Shadowloo forces stands here observing his students.
~
The instructor looks quite experienced in the fighting arts. He looks 
around the room making sure the students are doing their martial art 
drills correctly. He begins to scream commands to his students in hopes to
better their skills and strengths. He looks at you and creates a mocking
expressing on his face. He turns away slowly with a laugh and continues
his training.
~
