Entrance to Shadowloo~
This is Shadowloo, the fortress of the notorious M.Bison. From here you 
notice that all of Shadowloo is surrounded by a large wall and this 
looks like the only entrance. Shadowloo Officers are here making sure 
that there is no trouble within the area.
~
