#11609
Work Area~
Here is where the prisoners of Shadowloo do there work. This is part of the 
punishment for being an enemy of the Shadowloo. The prisoners weld steel 
into weapons, doors, almost anything. The weaker prisoners clean and help 
out the stronger prisoners do there work. A few prison guards are here 
making sure that no one tries to escape.
